          "description": "Apotheco Pharmacy Manhattan is good for dermatology prescriptions\u2014 they specialize in skin meds, so the pharmacists know their stuff and help get the lowest prices (branded or generic). Free delivery is convenient in the city, and they've coordinated with my derm office okay. It's 3 stars though because I've had delays on fills (waited extra days a couple times), and phone hold times can be long when calling for updates. Solid for specialized needs, but not the fastest\u2014better than chains for derm, but patience required.",
