          "description": "Fast and friendly delivery.  I liked that the delivery driver calls before he\u2019s there to make sure you\u2019re home.  The employees at the pharmacy were very nice and helpful with any questions I had.  The demeanor is very professional.  The delivery driver rode his bicycle in the frigid cold, wind, and rain at night to bring me my prescriptions - I was very appreciative.",
