          "description": "Honestly, this is the best pharmacy. Their customer service is amazing. When calling their store, I have never had to wait on hold longer than a couple minutes. They are super nice and understanding. I was able to get my medication delivered same-day at no extra charge. Definitely recommend! Thank you to all the workers at Apotheco for your great work!",
